data.description: Like New! Beautiful lake front, spacious home in a wonderful gated community. The home has been freshly and professionally painted, Newer beautiful wood look tile in living areas and Brand New carpet just installed. Included are a 2 year old water heater and BRAND NEW upstairs HVAC system. Cook with Gas in this home that features a spacious family room, formal living room, dinning room, downstairs and upstairs flex room, a huge master suite with walk in shower, Garden tub, double sinks and two spacious walk-in closets. Enjoy the start and end of your day relaxing on your screened porch gazing at the beautiful water view.NEW ROOF WILL BE INSTALLED PRIOR TO CLOSING!
